562
00:25:57,340 --> 00:25:58,660
Oh my.

563
00:26:00,810 --> 00:26:01,510
Ling Se,

564
00:26:03,540 --> 00:26:04,630
what Mother said

565
00:26:04,660 --> 00:26:05,340
was from

566
00:26:05,360 --> 00:26:06,890
