567
00:26:06,890 --> 00:26:08,150
Don’t take it to heart.

568
00:26:11,330 --> 00:26:12,400
I don't understand

569
00:26:12,490 --> 00:26:13,760
why no one is willing

570
00:26:13,790 --> 00:26:14,920
