574
00:26:19,670 --> 00:26:20,470
Young Master!

575
00:26:21,150 --> 00:26:21,620
Young Master!

576
00:26:21,620 --> 00:26:22,810
Young Master, bad news!

577
00:26:22,810 --> 00:26:24,030
You'd better go back to the shop and take a look.

578
00:26:24,030 --> 00:26:25,000
